:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:41:19.000Z","msg":"iPhone 11 無5G 😠"},{"pid":"f560df5c393c3b636fb9da242af70d92b9a6d998","tid":1598323,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"我想換咪換囉<br />\n咁都可以寫到篇文登去NYT<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e49fbca4d30d414bf0c0474e2a1a8b905e399a","tid":1598323,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:43:25.000Z","msg":"有錢既話用兩個月都要換"},{"pid":"cddc826c8cb07ad7efc069c542989d38f9dd8f8b","tid":1598323,"uid":70127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"56K已足夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7858e3c74fade5c348413d3fe042c40462b5ba","tid":1598323,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"用an機唔算理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db041a4318376d512c0e53deb9eee893bd7515f","tid":1598323,"uid":310752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:53:36.000Z","msg":"有錢想換就換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f35ff89dcded62ac2e57cf932cc6cc0db01a02","tid":1598323,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90af57d0babfedcf3e39a73537b7fec096de00eb","tid":1598323,"uid":113074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:40:32.000Z","msg":"呢一篇係每年都啱用<br />\n諾基亞都屌打蘋果呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:31:46.000Z","msg":"如今能跟 iPhone 相提並論的大螢幕觸控音樂手機不多，iPhone 已經第三年登上機皇的寶座，難道就沒有一款手機從 iPhone 手裡將機皇的寶座搶回來嗎？ Nokia 大會上最先發佈的這款 Nokia X6 就具備這樣的實力。<br />\nNokia X6 有紅黑、藍白兩種顏色可供選擇，該機採用 Symbian OS v9.4 操作系統，基於 S60 5th Edition 平台。X6 的機身厚度只有 13.8mm，相比前作 N97、5800 XpressMusic 都要薄很多，相比 iPhone 還是略厚。另外，X6 能連續播放音樂達 35 小時，與 iPhone 相當。<br />\n<br />\n定位高端市場的 X6，配備 500 萬像素的「卡爾‧蔡司」自動對焦攝頭以及雙 LED 閃光燈，這一點遠勝於 iPhone。X6 有效工作頻率為 433MHz 的中央處理器，以及 32GB 機身存儲空間，與 iPhone 旗鼓相當。不過 X6 省略了 micro SD（T-Flash）存儲卡插槽，同時 1600 萬色、360 x 640 解像度 TFT 觸控螢幕，其面積由 3.5 吋降為 3.2 吋。<br />\n<br />\n另外，X6 還預裝 Ovi 商店，並支援 Come With Music 服務。Ovi 商店是 Nokia 重點打造的商店軟件，儘管目前還比不上 Apple 的 App Store，但是將來全面的 Ovi 服務，將有機會全面超越 App Store。"}]}